'''Chubar''' was a character from an animated children's [[Hologram/Legends|holoprogram]] series, voiced by famed child actor [[Garik Loran|Garik "Face" Loran]]. Chubar was a [[Bilar]], and the exceptionally intelligent pet of a young [[Human/Legends|Human]] girl. The character was the inspiration for [[Project Chubar]], an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] program to modify [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]] and members of other non-[[Human/Legends|Human]] species to think and behave like Humans.

